name: AnimeSwap
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
1. The token of AnimeSwap protocol, deployed on Aptos Mainnet
2. AnimeSwap protocol is an open AMM & DeFi protocol on Aptos, everyone could create pair and add liquidity, swap, or farm.
3. Deployed on Aptos at Day0 2022/10/19, ANI token launching at 2022/11/10.
4. Deployed on Sui (using Move, the same contract language as Aptos), more collaboration and listings https://docs.animeswap.org/docs/updates/2023
5. Check https://docs.animeswap.org/docs/tutorial/Tokenomics#usages
